snippet.textDisplay: So beautiful! I'm really thankful to Cirque du Soleil, you were able to lighten my energy in a way that only art does. Made my laugh, made me cry, mesmerized me... it's incredible to have this kind of good energy inside my house during such a difficult moment. I'm Brazilian, and our own president doesn't seem to recognize how serious is the situation we're living, but you guys did, and did the best you could for all of us. Thank you, thank you.

snippet.textDisplay: It was years after I saw the show that I looked up the English translation of "Alegria".  I do a little French, mostly when relaxed by a couple of glasses of wine (Doesn't have to even be French wine) but I guess then my inhibitions disappear.  Yes, I did a lot of business in France but they all speak more English than I speak French, and their English is usually more precise than mine.
